data.description: LOOKING FOR PLENTY OF SPACE? THIS 2 STORY, 4 BEDROOM, 2.5 BATH HOME HAS ALL THE SPACE YOU WILL NEED! PLENTY OF STORAGE, BEAUTIFUL LIGHT FIXTURES, EACH ROOM COMES WITH A GREAT SIZE CLOSET AS WELL AS 2 WALK-IN CLOSETS IN THE OWNER SUITE. KITCHEN IS FULLY EQUIPPED, HAS 2 PANTRIES, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, KITCHEN ISLAND AND GORGEOUS TILED BACKSPLASH. NEW LVP FLOORING IN DINING AND KITCHEN, RENOVATED BATHROOM (CABINET). BACKS TO WOODED AREA FOR PRIVACYAND BACK YARD PARTIALLY FENCED. LOCATED IN THE POPULAR COMMUNITY OF PINE BLUFF IN A CUL-DE-SAC. NEW HVAC 2021! WATER HEATER ONLY 1 YR OLD! SELLER OFFERING AMERICAN HOME SHIELD HOME WARRANTY. SELLER HAS A 2.75% ASSUMABLE VA LOAN. APPROXIMATELY 1 MILE FROM THE I-95 INTERSTATE AND ABOUT 25 MINUTES TO JACKSONVILLE INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT. VERY CLOSE TO SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS AND KINGS BAY NAVAL SUBMARINE BASE. APPROXIMATELY 45 MINUTES TO FLETC. NESTLED BETWEEN JACKSONVILLE, FL AND BRUNSWICK, GA, JEKYLL ISLAND AND SAINT SIMONS ISLAND AND THE BEAUTIFUL, SANDY BEACHES OF FERNANDINA BEACH, FL SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY! HOMES DO NOT LAST LONG IN THIS COMMUNITY!
